OL,3,CFire causes 'severe' disruption to
OL,4,Crail lines
OL,6,FA fire has caused "severe" disruption
OL,7,Fto the rail network around Cardiff
OL,8,FCentral.
OL,10,FNetwork Rail have confirmed that a
OL,11,Ffire at an electrical substation next
OL,12,Fto a railway track in the St Brides
OL,13,Farea - between Newport and Cardiff
OL,14,FCentral - on Sunday, May 4, has closed
OL,15,Ftwo railway lines.
OL,17,FThe fire has been extinguished, but
OL,18,Fhas caused damage to the overhead line
OL,19,Fand signalling equipment which
OL,20,Frequires the lines to be closed to
OL,21,Frepair.
