OL,3,CFire causes 'severe' disruption to
OL,4,Crail lines
OL,6,FIn an update on their website, Network
OL,7,FRail said that the fire has resulted
OL,8,Fin "severe disruption across the south
OL,9,Fof Wales, with two of the four lines
OL,10,Fremaining closed whilst repair work
OL,11,Fcontinues."
OL,13,FA limited service of two trains in
OL,14,Feach direction every hour is able to
OL,15,Foperate between Newport and Cardiff
OL,16,FCentral, at a reduced speed.
OL,18,FHowever, trains between these stations
OL,19,Fcould be cancelled, delayed by up to
OL,20,F60 minutes or revised.
