OL,3,CFire causes 'severe' disruption to
OL,4,Crail lines
OL,6,FThe major disruption is expected to
OL,7,Fcontinue to impact services until the
OL,8,Fend of the day on Tuesday, May 6,
OL,9,Fwhile repair work is ongoing.
OL,11,FServices by Transport for Wales, Great
OL,12,FWestern Railway and CrossCountry
OL,13,FRailway across dozens of routes in
OL,14,FSouth Wales and the South West of
OL,15,FEngland have been impacted by the
OL,16,Fincident. Customers are urged to check
OL,17,Ftheir journey details before
OL,18,Ftravelling.
